Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}突然出现在东京市中心的神秘物体使交通网络中断
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.03,0:02:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}首都地区的交通完全瘫痪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}附近的居民请千万不要靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.24,0:02:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}在没确定情况之前 存在着未知的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.15,0:02:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}这件事已变成了可怕的局势
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}有没有什么对策
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.89,0:02:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}在还不知道那个巨大的邪恶黑水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}到底有拥有多大力量之前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}不多搜集一些资料 是没有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.96,0:02:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}现在也只能等待出去调查的小卫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}和亚提密斯带着结果回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.05,0:02:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}在那之前只好在这里待机了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.79,0:02:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}小小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:02:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}听起来非常危险 太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.29,0:03:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}我们留在这里避难好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}妈妈 那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}什么？这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.69,0:03:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}一二三
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.03,0:03:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}讨厌 为什么会多一个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}奇怪 我以为大家在一起这么多杯刚刚好…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.31,0:03:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.98,0:03:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}露娜比消失之后 妈妈他们应该不记得小小兔才是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}看来在记忆中的某处还残留着一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.98,0:03:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}露娜 你说我是贪心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}小小兔不在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.26,0:03:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}应该只是恢复原来的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.03,0:03:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}但是我总觉得这个房子好空旷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}打起精神来 小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.61,0:04:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}小丽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}我们团结起来 小小兔一定能恢复原来一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.87,0:04:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}也对 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.83,0:04:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}虚无 寂静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.39,0:04:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}听从我的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}向全知全能的死亡幻影发誓忠诚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.14,0:04:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}统治宇宙的不是做短暂梦想的狄曼特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.89,0:04:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}是拥有绝对性力量的死亡幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.06,0:04:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}愚蠢的狄曼特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}你只需要在平静之中引起混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}而我们也就是这个世界的霸者死亡幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.95,0:04:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}是为了引发宇宙的混沌虚无
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:05:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}把这些生命的污秽物体在宇宙中完全抹杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.35,0:05:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.35,0:05:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}他只是利用了哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.39,0:05:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}可恶的韦斯曼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}这种异常高的能源
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.62,0:05:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}也是他干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.05,0:05:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}照这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}不能再让反应炉失控下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}萨菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}韦斯曼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.45,0:06:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}立刻把它恢复原状
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}你没资格命令我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.35,0:06:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}等跟哥哥谈过之后 再决定怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}向你下命令的是统治宇宙的死亡幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}违抗死亡幻影旨意的人 就意味着死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}刚才你一直在说的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.46,0:06:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}死亡幻影到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.21,0:06:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}使宇宙回归美丽寂静透明虚无的至高无上的神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}它会把像你们这些不洁的生命体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}在宇宙之中完全消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.56,0:06:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}你…你到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.19,0:06:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}现在还不是说出来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}韦斯曼 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:06:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}你就无知地去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}算了 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}我知道他要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}黑暗之门成长得顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.49,0:07:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}再过不久
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}反应炉的能源到达颠峰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}再把那股能源引导过来…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}这个世界会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}未来将会产生巨大的改变
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}大家冷静 大家冷静的撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.87,0:07:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}好像真的展开行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}姐姐 我们也去避难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:07:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}也对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.59,0:08:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.66,0:08:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}哥哥 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}照这样下去 会被韦斯曼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}是草的香味…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.82,0:08:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}真怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}哥哥 是花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}嗯 很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}好难得哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}但是在奈美希斯只有这么小的花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}所以 总有一天我们会进攻驱逐我们的地球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.59,0:08:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}得到一望无际的花圃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}嗯 哥哥一定办得到的 一定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}好了 走吧 王子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}韦斯曼 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.09,0:09:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.28,0:09:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}不行 别去他身边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}哥哥 哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}你醒了 萨菲尔王子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}佩茨 你是佩茨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.86,0:09:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}我的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}说起来你们背叛我们后 住在这个世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}我早就有觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.18,0:09:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}但是 请放过妹妹们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}要处罚的 我一个就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:10:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}我不是为了那件事来这个世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.30,0:10:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}佩茨姐姐不是讨厌男人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.99,0:10:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}我们不必逃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.43,0:10:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}他是来处罚我们的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}我想应该不会有事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}暂时别去打扰他们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}姐姐一直喜欢萨菲尔王子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}萨菲尔发疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}他拔掉反应炉的控制面板使反应炉停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.72,0:10:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}萨菲尔是逃到这个世界的叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.57,0:10:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}杀死他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.07,0:10:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}然后把控制面板抢回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}萨菲尔不可能做那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.56,0:11:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}那么你是打算要终止计划了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}这件任务交给我Black Lady来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}萨菲尔会背叛我？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.13,0:11:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}好了 请用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.11,0:11:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}你变了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.91,0:11:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}不知该怎么形容…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}现在这样与你在一起心里安详多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}我们从水手月亮她们那学到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.00,0:12:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}身为一个人类应该拥有的善良与信任
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}水手月亮？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.34,0:12:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}这个世界跟以前在奈美希斯的时候比起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}虽有很多不方便的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}但是也充满了温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}我们觉得心灵受到了拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}相信人 互相关爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.67,0:12:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}是非常美好的一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.01,0:12:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}我们所做的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}真的正确吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}我们想创造的未来是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}我们不择手段地去报复 也许都是受韦斯曼的控制
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:12:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}萨菲尔王子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:13:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}我得赶快走…赶快…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}萨菲尔王子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}我必须快点见哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}赶快…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}你还是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}心中只想着狄曼特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}佩茨 拿我的上衣来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.22,0:13:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}不行 就这样的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.28,0:13:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}一刻也好我必须赶快通知他 韦斯曼真正的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.02,0:13:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}佩茨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}你的伤 是被谁弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}我大概也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}你拖着受伤的身体去找狄曼特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.63,0:13:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}你会…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}佩茨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}你 如果 如果发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}我必须去呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}如果你发现你的妹妹们还在走着错误的路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:13:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}你也不能对她们置之不理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}狄曼特王子是我唯一的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.06,0:14:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}不用担心 我只是找他谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}事情结束后 我会再次回来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.27,0:14:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}萨菲尔王子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.45,0:14:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}为了那个时刻 这件外套我就留给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}为什么姐姐让他一个人离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}他那伤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.38,0:14:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}现在追上去还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}现在的我们 做得了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}我们已经没有以前那种力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.09,0:14:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}只会当他的绊脚石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}能做的只有等待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:14:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}喂 月野公馆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.17,0:14:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}可安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.36,0:15:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}小兔 求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}你自己送上门来 替我省了寻找的功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}让开 Black Lady 我有事找我哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.77,0:15:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}在那之前你得先死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.89,0:15:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}水手月亮？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.62,0:15:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}你们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}不行 小小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.91,0:15:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}不可以伤害他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}你被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}为什么你还不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}你这样想就大错了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}我是依我自己的意志在行动的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}求求你 快点清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}烦死了 露娜比 变化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.33,0:16:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}小小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:11.18,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1C71FD&}新月光束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}还没行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.44,0:16:18.68,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFDC228&}Bubble…Spray!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}好了 萨菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}趁现在快去找狄曼特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}为什么你们对我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}详情的我们也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.57,0:16:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}是可安她们叫我们来救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}笨蛋 这也可能是陷阱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}是啊 可是因为某某人的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}我们都变成呆子了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}就算是敌人 我们也喜欢相信她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.71,0:16:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}特别是水手月亮那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.50,0:16:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}你们以为这样就能封锁住我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.36,0:17:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}小小兔 快恢复本性
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.13,0:17:09.41,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}月水晶力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.37,0:17:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}同一招是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}来 看招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.41,0:17:24.04,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1C71FD&}爱神维纳斯锁链…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}不要管我 去救她们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.77,0:17:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}可…可是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.03,0:17:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}不用担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}我找到要谈话的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.07,0:17:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}好了 快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.16,0:17:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}萨菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.85,0:17:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}萨菲尔 为何背叛我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.34,0:18:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}我没有背叛你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.58,0:18:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.66,0:18:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}我们都被韦斯曼给骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.55,0:18:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}你在胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.30,0:18:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}萨菲尔 妨碍计划的人就算是你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}哥哥 这个计划可能是个大错误
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.36,0:18:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}我们想做的事情应该不是这样的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}我们只是被利用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.70,0:18:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.05,0:18:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}罗罗嗦嗦的吵死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}这个玫瑰是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}住手 小小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.08,0:18:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}狄曼特 听萨菲尔说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.13,0:18:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}你弟弟在未来看到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}好好的听一听
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}萨菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:18:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}到底在未来发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.02,0:18:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.83,0:19:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.86,0:19:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}萨…萨菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}韦斯曼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}叛徒萨菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}处死叛徒用不着玷污王子尊贵的手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.58,0:19:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.32,0:19:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}韦斯曼连未来都想毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.01,0:19:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}他的目的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}慢着 韦斯曼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}萨菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}萨菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.59,0:19:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}愚蠢的萨菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}竟然被水手战士所骗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.53,0:20:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}在胡言乱语
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}Black Lady和狄曼特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.94,0:20:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}跟那些小女生们总有一天会再做个了结的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.66,0:20:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}萨菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.46,0:20:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}对不起 我没能保护他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}佩茨 对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.59,0:20:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}萨菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.99,0:20:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}不行 不可以死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.35,0:20:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}佩茨呢 佩茨怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.02,0:20:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}萨菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}狄曼特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:20:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}萨菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}韦斯曼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.54,0:21:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.67,0:21:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.28,0:21:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}送他走的时候 我就知道事情会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}萨菲尔王子 永远在我心中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.48,0:21:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}与他最后送给我的微笑一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.23,0:22:21.56,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1}不管面临什么困难
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.57,0:22:24.53,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1}绝对都不能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.78,0:22:28.07,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1}没错 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.08,0:22:31.74,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1}青春可爱少女的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.75,0:22:35.24,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1}为了将来的某一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.25,0:22:38.38,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1}以后最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.63,0:22:45.22,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1}抬起头来扑到他的怀里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.97,0:22:52.56,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1}在平然心痛伤口的深处
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.81,0:22:58.85,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1}恋爱的幼苗开始觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.85,0:23:02.31,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1}什么都不用怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.32,0:23:05.73,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1}惊险刺激也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.74,0:23:09.57,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1}怀抱自己的大梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.58,0:23:15.00,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1}微风涣涣的向前走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.96,0:23:19.50,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1}完成内心深处的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.50,0:23:22.92,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1}当个努力的人也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:26.71,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1}偶尔会伤心流泪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.71,0:23:32.43,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp1}也要抬起头继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.02,0:23:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}给我们制造麻烦的美丽魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.69,0:23:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}水手月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.25,0:23:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}现在我要让你以爱的忠诚向我发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.65,0:23:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}请想想萨菲尔要向你传达的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.20,0:23:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}狄曼特 如果你明白真正的爱的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.75,0:23:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}我们一定能互相理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.35,0:24:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}美少女战士 水手月亮 R
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.35,0:24:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}相信爱和未来 小兔的决心
